headline: 2 Reasons to Like YUM and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Over the past six months, Yum! Brands has been a great trade. While the S&P 500 was flat, the stock price has climbed by 10.9% to $146.51 per share. This performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
